name: Music Player Inspired by Caler Edwards
description:
Designed and prototyped in Figma as against using Adobe XD and without any third party app for the prototyping. This is just to proof that Figma is far more advance and give you granular control of the elements in your design.


Check out Caler on https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JE-EsLhmlkU&t=75s
